ZH: 我们在海边租了一艘游艇。
EN: We rented a yacht by the seaside.

ZH: 他花了大笔钱买了一艘名贵的游艇。
EN: He spent a lot of money buying an expensive yacht.

ZH: 我们一家人一起在游艇上度过了一个美好的下午。
EN: Our family spent a wonderful afternoon together on the yacht.

ZH: 游艇上的乘客们欣赏着美丽的海景。
EN: The passengers on the yacht were enjoying the beautiful sea view.

ZH: 那艘游艇是他的珍贵财产之一。
EN: That yacht is one of his precious possessions.

ZH: 游艇在海上飘荡，感觉特别自由。
EN: The yacht drifted on the sea, feeling particularly free.

ZH: 那艘游艇拥有最新的航行技术。
EN: That yacht has the latest sailing technology.

ZH: 游艇上的厨师做出了一道道美味的海鲜菜肴。
EN: The chef on the yacht cooked delicious seafood dishes.

ZH: 游艇上提供了各种各样的水上运动项目。
EN: The yacht offered a variety of water sports activities.

ZH: 我梦想拥有一艘舒适豪华的游艇。
EN: I dream of owning a comfortable and luxurious yacht.

ZH: 游艇上的设施非常齐全。
EN: The facilities on the yacht are very complete.

ZH: 游艇在波光粼粼的海面上飘荡。
EN: The yacht drifted on the sparkling sea.

ZH: 那艘游艇非常昂贵，不是一般人能负担得起的。
EN: That yacht is very expensive and not affordable for ordinary people.

ZH: 游艇上有专门的船员负责操纵。
EN: There are dedicated crew members on the yacht responsible for navigation.

ZH: 游艇驶向遥远的海岸线。
EN: The yacht sailed towards the distant coastline.

ZH: 游艇上有一个露天阳台，可以欣赏美景。
EN: The yacht has an open-air deck where you can enjoy the beautiful scenery.

ZH: 我们在游艇上举办了一个盛大的生日派对。
EN: We hosted a grand birthday party on the yacht.

ZH: 游艇是奢华旅游的象征之一。
EN: Yachts are a symbol of luxury travel.

ZH: 游艇上的餐厅提供美味的海鲜大餐。
EN: The restaurant on the yacht offers delicious seafood meals.

ZH: 游艇上的客房装饰豪华舒适。
EN: The rooms on the yacht are luxuriously decorated and comfortable.
